I guess I should warn all you guys to be sure that you don't have level numbers
that overlap the level numbers of other peoples' levels.  With the rush of
people
preparing levels to be released, this is a must.  I'd be happy to maintain some
kind of a list somewhere on the web that says exactly what levels are taken,
and where they can be acquired.  Thoughts?

I just figured that with everyone making levels, the overlapping of the numbers
might end up being a concern.

-Chris/Shayd
